In [78]:

```python
fig = plt.figure()
ax1, ax2, ax3, ax4 = fig.add_subplot(4, 1, 1), fig.add_subplot(4, 1, 2), fig.add_subplot(4, 1, 3), fig.add_subplot(4, 1, 4)
ax1_2, ax2_2, ax3_2, ax4_2 = ax1.twinx(), ax2.twinx(), ax3.twinx(), ax4.twinx()

# 'USGBR10', 'USDJPY', 'EUR','AUD','CODIVUSD'
t = date_time
[l1, l2, l3, l4, l5] = df.columns
[a1, a2, a3, a4, a5] = df.columns
y1, y2, y3, y4, y5 = [ df[name] for name in [a1, a2, a3, a4, a5] ]

c1,c2,c3,c4 = "#1f77b4","#ff7f0e","#2ca02c","#d62728"      # 各プロットの色
c5 = "#9467bd"
# ['#1f77b4','#ff7f0e','#2ca02c','#d62728','#9467bd','#8c564b','#e377c2','#7f7f7f','#bcbd22','#17becf']

ax1.plot(t, y1, color=c1, label=l1)
ax2.plot(t, y2, color=c2, label=l2)
ax3.plot(t, y3, color=c3, label=l3)
ax4.plot(t, y4, color=c4, label=l4)
ax1_2.plot(t, y5, color=c5, label=l1)
ax2_2.plot(t, y5, color=c5, label=l2)
ax3_2.plot(t, y5, color=c5, label=l3)
ax4_2.plot(t, y5, color=c5, label=l4)

ax1.set_title('CODIV vs USDJPY')

fig.tight_layout()              #レイアウトの設定
plt.show()
```
